name: LogLevel
description: The output log level of the SDK.

parameters.None: 0: Do not output any log information.

parameters.Info:
0x0001: (Default) Output FATAL, ERROR,
                        WARN, and INFO level log information. We
                        recommend setting your log filter as this level.

parameters.Warn:
0x0002: Output FATAL, ERROR, and WARN level
                        log information.

parameters.Error: 0x0004: Output FATAL and ERROR level log information.
